                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6615" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1677</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9795 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“一无是处”到“一鸣惊人”：一鸣电器隐形冠军之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">No rains it pours: Yiming Electric’s way to hidden champion</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘闲月，郑文智，冯琼凤，吴宇磊，王子宁，汪秋丽，黄珊玲，李阳尧，郑思琦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华侨大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">泉州市一鸣交通电器有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">电子工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">隐形冠军；专精特新；聚集战略；“T型战略”；“第二曲线战略”；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hidden champion; Specialized and innovative enterprises; Agglomeration Strategy; T-Strategy; Second Curve Strategy</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">隐形冠军具有较高的市场占有率和领导力、较强的竞争优势和影响力，已成为我国政府扶持、企业关心的热点现象，“专精特新”、“小巨人”、“高新技术企业”、“单项冠军”、“领航企业”等相关名词频繁出现在学术文献、媒体报道和政府文件中。然而，冠军的光环下隐藏着较多的馅饼和陷阱，成长中有较多的故事和事故：如何协调“大”与“小”、“全”与“精”、眼前与长远、区域化与全球化、坚守与创新之间的矛盾？本案例以福建省泉州市一鸣交通电器有限公司为分析对象，描述了公司从合资企业口中“一无是处”的民营小企业成长为“一鸣惊人”的世界级隐形冠军过程中的关键事件、决策情境。案例最大程度上还原公司持续成长的历程，旨在帮助学生们从显性的战略行为、路径和组合中逆向思考公司的战略思维与内在逻辑，培养学生的辩证思维、悖论思维和战略性、哲学性思考的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> Hidden champion have high market share, effective leadership, strong competitive advantage and influence. It has supported by the government and enterprises in our country. &quot;single champion&quot;, &quot;high-tech enterprises&quot; and other related terms frequently appear in academic literature, media reports and government documents. However, there are many traps and accidents in growth: how to coordinate the contradictory relationship between &quot;big&quot; and &quot;small&quot;, &quot;full&quot; and &quot;streamline&quot;, immediate and long-term, regionalization and globalization, persistence and innovation? This case describes Yiming Electric’s key events and decision-making situations in the process of the company&#39;s growth from a &quot;no good&quot; private small enterprise to a &quot;blockbuster&quot; world hidden champion. This case describes the company&#39;s continuous growth process that aims to help students reverse the company&#39;s strategy, internal logic from explicit strategic behaviors, paths and combinations, and cultivates students&#39; dialectical thinking, paradox thinking and the ability to philosophical thinking.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">隐形冠军企业的定义与特质；聚焦战略；国际化战略；相关多元化（需求协同型）；“T型战略”；“第二曲线战略”</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
